HEADWORD: Flammeous
<hw>Flam"me*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>flammeus</ets> from <ets>flamma</ets> flame.]</ety> <def>Pertaining
to, consisting of, or resembling, flame.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

